  ARRAY['The lowest direct-cash entry point among the IRA specialists in this comparison, at $2,000','Segregated-only storage — assets are never commingled with other customers'', a real differentiator versus lower-cost competitors','One of the highest Trustpilot scores in this comparison: 4.9/5 from 783 reviews, plus only 4-5 BBB complaints in 3 years']::text[],
  ARRAY['A flat $275/yr fee is confirmed, but the metal premium itself is still phone-quoted, same as every IRA specialist here','Narrower independent editorial coverage than Augusta, Goldco, American Hartford Gold, or Birch Gold','"Royal Survival Packs" are advertised but were not independently verified in this research']::text[],
  '{"cost":7.8,"features":8.0,"ux":8.2,"support":8.0}'::jsonb,
  'The lowest cash entry point, with segregated-only storage as a real differentiator',
  'Noble Gold Investments has the lowest direct-cash entry point among the five gold IRA specialists in this comparison at $2,000 (versus $20,000 for an IRA rollover), and it offers segregated-only storage — assets are never pooled with other customers'' metal, a real differentiator versus commingled-storage competitors. It confirms a flat $275/year IRA fee ($125 custodial + $150 segregated storage) directly on its own support page, and carries one of the highest Trustpilot scores in this comparison at 4.9/5 from 783 reviews, plus only 4-5 BBB complaints in 3 years. Independent editorial coverage is narrower than the larger IRA specialists in this comparison.',
  false, NULL, 'https://noblegoldinvestments.com/', false, 'Lowest cash entry point + segregated-only storage', 3,
